_sText:
This map is similar to fy_iceworld except with a few changes.  There are reloading catapults that launch exploding watermelons across the map, along with a watermelon dropper on the tops of 4 center columns in the map.

There is a buyzone in the middle, over some breakable ice that covers an underwater tunnel.

I recommend using sv_turbophysics "1" so you can push the melons around. (Especially at the top, you can push them off in any direction with turbo physics.)
